{"tid":1028329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人口達748萬人　去年增加6.9萬   4.23萬人持單程證來港","createTime":"2019-02-19T11:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T15:58:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8832261ceba6eaf7a7c4132f441b4ef2c6aff9b","tid":1028329,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190219/photo/bkn-20190219163030524-0219_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190219193340\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190219%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190219163030524-0219_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190219193340&h=a1e63159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港去年底人口上升至約7,482,500人，增加69,400人。統計處今天(19日)公布去年香港人口的臨時數字又顯示，去年持單程證來港的新移民有42,300人，較2017年的4.7萬人減少4700。內地新移民能說廣東話的比例下跌，由2008年第三季84.3%，降至去年第三季約68.9%。<br />\n<br />\n內地新移民近日被指搶佔港人房屋資源，惟民政事務總署的調查結果則提供「另類」角度讓人思考。截至去年第三季，該署訪問9329內地新移民，顯示47.6%受訪者居於公屋，較13年同期54.8%低；同期，居於私人永久性房屋的受訪者則有41.6%，較2013年同期31.1%高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190219/bkn-20190219163030524-0219_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190219%2Fbkn-20190219163030524-0219_00822_001.html&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZzbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=96894d94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190219/bkn-20190219163030524-0219_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dd6865c69966bf3825c85c3c271d635358df9f86","tid":1028329,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"換血快到..."},{"pid":"d0692483ea90d8579b4c91afbfb59625d70d8dee","tid":1028329,"uid":3093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:08:35.000Z","msg":"香港身分證係咪全宇宙最易攞？"},{"pid":"54dd3468134bdc351c2110a210f9980ae8d82ef4","tid":1028329,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets